Package com.chupacadabra.evolution.engine

This package contains the core optimizer components.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DifferentialEvolutionReceiver
    Receiver interface for engine commands.
    Initialization
    Engine initialization strategy.
    Iteration
    Iteration strategy for the engine.
    PoolCreation
    Pool creation strategy for the engine.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractIndexCommand
    Base class for the index commands.
    CountDownCommand
    This command counts down a latch once an underlying task completes.
    CreateChildCandidateTask
    Callable task to create a child candidate.
    DifferentialEvolutionEngine
    The core differential evolution optimization engine.
    DirectInitialization
    Direct initialization.
    DirectIteration
    Direct iteration.
    ExecutorInitialization
    Executor-based initialization strategy.
    ExecutorIteration
    Executor-based iteration.
    ForkJoinDifferentialEvolutionOptimizer
    An optimizer that uses a fork-join pool to spawn tasks.
    InitializeIndexCommand
    Command to initialize a particular index in the current pool with a random feasible candidate.
    IterateIndexCommand
    Iterate index command.
    NoOpLockingPoolCreation
    Pool creator that returns a pool that does no actual locking.
    ReadWriteLockPoolCreation
    Read-write lock pool creator.
    ReportExceptionCommand
    Exception reporting command.
